data.description: Perfect starter home or rental for that traveling nurse.  There's alley access with entry to single car garage with automatic garage door opener.  Completely fenced.  Big trees in front of home providing great shade on those hot days.  Easy access to freeway and downtown.  Home is adorable and there is also a shed for storage. Fresh paint and floors, updated bathroom, newer roof with recent blown in insulation, updated electrical.
